For example, bytes=0-9 indicates that you want to copy the first ten bytes of the source. You can copy a range only if the source object is greater than 5 MB.

id: Wait until 200 response is received when polling with head-bucket.  It will poll every 5 seconds until a successful state has been reached. This will exit with a return code of 255 after 20 failed checks.
translation: Espere hasta recibir la respuesta 200 cuando sondee con head-bucket.  Se sondeará cada 5 segundos hasta alcanzar un estado correcto. Esto provocará una salida con un código de retorno 255 después de 20 comprobaciones con error.

id: Wait until 200 response is received when polling with head-object.  It will poll every 5 seconds until a successful state has been reached.  This will exit with a return code of 255 after 20 failed checks.

id: Wait until a particular condition is satisfied.  Each subcommand polls an API until the listed requirement is met.
translation: Espere hasta que se satisfaga una condición determinada.  Cada submandato sondea una API hasta cumplir el requisito de la lista.

id: Your proposed upload is smaller than the minimum allowed size. File parts must be greater than 5 MB in size, except for the last part.
translation: Su carga propuesta es más pequeña que el tamaño mínimo permitido. Las partes del archivo deben tener un tamaño superior a 5 MB, excepto la última parte.

id: `SIZE` of the body in bytes. This parameter is useful when the size of the body cannot be determined automatically.
translation: `SIZE` del cuerpo en bytes. Este parámetro es útil cuando el tamaño del cuerpo no se puede determinar automáticamente.
